data.text: A curated list of awesome MicroPython libraries, frameworks, software and resources.
Other places you can look for MicroPython Libraries:
Programming with MicroPython: Embedded Programming with Microcontrollers and Python
MicroPython for the Internet of Things: A Beginner's Guide to Programming with Python on Microcontrollers
Python for Microcontrollers: Getting Started with MicroPython
Advanced Programming in MicroPython By Example
I will keep some pull requests open if I'm not sure whether those libraries are awesome, you could vote for them by adding 👍 to them.
